BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:sd4dX_onSf8u9tWIg9_5k
SUMMARY:Johnny &amp\; Reg @ Perihelion Brewery
DTSTAMP:20260413T004142Z
DTSTART:20260722T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:Johnny & Reg grew from late-night jam sessions and a shared lov
	e of funky\, soulful music. Their sound drifts through blue notes and groo
	ves\, equal parts raw and refined. It carries the dust of back roads and t
	he glow of late-night campfires — acoustic wanderers moving from town to t
	own with a suitcase of blues\, jazz-tinged melodies\, and stories gathered
	 along the way. The sound leans into raw wood and warm strings\, equal par
	ts grit and grace\, always shaped by the places they pass through. Eclecti
	c\, earthy\, and effortlessly heartfelt.With tight harmonies\, weathered r
	hythms\, and a laid-back charm\, they will bring a rich\, rootsy energy to
	 Perihelion’s outdoor Patio!\n\nhttps://www.perihelion.beer/events/2026/7/
	21/johnny-amp-red-perihelion-brewery\n\nFrom Perihelion Brewery
URL:https://www.perihelion.beer/events/2026/7/21/johnny-amp-red-perihelion-
	brewery
LOCATION:Perihelion Brewery\, 2800 16th Ave South\, Seattle\, WA 98144
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:all-events
CATEGORIES:Perihelion Brewery
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
