DESCRIPTION:Michigan native\, now Seattle-based\, Sarah Brunner is a full t
	ime musician\, both solo and with her band The Hipocrats. With influences 
	ranging from Brandi Carlile\, to Sam Smith to The Lumineers\, she uses rhy
	thm guitar just as much as a vocal melody to define a song.We are excited 
	to have Sarah at Perihelion from 7-9pm for some lovely live music.\n\nhttp
